1. *Toma* je juče kupio novu knjigu. (*Toma* bought a new book yesterday.)
2. Ovaj roman je napisao *Toma* Andrić. (This novel was written by *Toma* Andrić.)
3. *Toma* je najbolji student na fakultetu. (*Toma* is the best student at the faculty.)
4. Njihov sin se zove *Toma*. (Their son's name is *Toma*.)
5. Molim *Tomu* da mi pozajmi olovku. (I'm asking *Toma* to lend me a pen.)
6. Kada *Toma* putuje, uvek sa sobom nosi svoj laptop. (When *Toma* travels, he always carries his laptop with him.)
7. *Toma* je dobar prijatelj koji uvek stoji uz mene. (*Toma* is a good friend who always stands by me.)
8. Kuća koju su sagradili *Toma* i Jelena je prelepa. (The house that *Toma* and Jelena built is beautiful.)
9. *Toma* je izuzetan sportista, uspešan i u trčanju i u plivanju. (*Toma* is an exceptional athlete, successful both in running and swimming.)
10. Znam da *Toma* voli da putuje, ali ne znam gde trenutno boravi. (I know that *Toma* likes to travel, but I don't know where he currently resides.)